Chordate:


He smiled as Feline agreed to wait, and sat down in his chair.  He walked 
over to her.  

"Well, basically, I let people in, I can work the base defenses.  I can send 
long distance comm. transmissions.  I do quite a lot of stuff." he pressed a 
few buttons, deactivating the sprinkler systems and flame retardent foam, 
activating a few drainage systems in the floors of "Bright Blade's room" and 
the hall near it.

"Maybe in a few days I'll show you how to use it."
